Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.79,0:00:08.60,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I hate this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.67,0:00:13.28,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's full of all the memories I want to forget about.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.78,0:00:22.55,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Go to school every day, chat with friends, and then\Nreturn to a home that I'd rather not go back to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.91,0:00:27.46,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Will doing this ever give way to change?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.11,0:00:32.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Will that day come?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.10,0:00:50.20,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Anpan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.69,0:00:53.93,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Do you like this school?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.32,0:00:57.40,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I really, really love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.72,0:01:01.71,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But nothing can stay unchanged.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.54,0:01:04.22,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,A girl I've never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.74,0:01:06.83,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The words weren't directed at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.55,0:01:11.54,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She must be talking to someone within her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.54,0:01:15.24,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Fun things… Happy things…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.23,0:01:18.94,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,They can't all possibly remain the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.94,0:01:21.97,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Even so, can you keep on loving this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.73,0:01:25.01,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Just find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:41.61,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Just find new fun and happy things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.92,0:01:45.38,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Come on, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.23,0:01:53.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We start to walk up…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.71,0:01:58.32,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,…the long, long, uphill climb.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.49,0:03:34.14,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Ramune's pretty nostalgic, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:41.95,Default,Rug,0,0,0,,Have you learned your lesson now, Sunohara?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:44.63,Default,Rug,0,0,0,,Stop listening to your music so damn loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.63,0:03:47.79,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,But if I don't listen to it like that, I can't get rolling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.79,0:03:48.94,Default,Rug,0,0,0,,Scrum!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:52.68,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,They don't get tired of doing that every day, do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.68,0:03:55.53,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Okazaki! Stop watching and help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.53,0:03:57.01,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll get infected by your idiocy, so no.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.01,0:03:59.13,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You're so heartless!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.73,0:04:14.50,Default,Rug,0,0,0,,Try!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:17.57,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.37,0:04:20.38,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Break it up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.80,0:04:24.30,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,For crying out loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.30,0:04:27.30,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I'm the one that has to deal with\Nthe complaints from the neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:30.13,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Dorm mother sounds like a tough job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.13,0:04:34.09,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Misae-san… Come save me earlier, please…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.09,0:04:36.26,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,You're the one at fault, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.26,0:04:38.55,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Why don't you learn your lesson?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.55,0:04:39.40,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:43.39,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(957.333,414)}Episode 1
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:43.39,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(965.333,724.5)}At the Hill Where the Cherry Blossoms Fall
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.12,0:04:43.40,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Damn that rugby club.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:46.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,They'll never hear you if you mumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.58,0:04:48.86,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Damn that rugby club!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.86,0:04:50.70,Default,Rug,0,0,0,,Who just said that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.13,0:04:54.11,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Are you trying to kill me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.11,0:04:55.84,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're wimping out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.84,0:04:58.53,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be if it was just me against one of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.53,0:05:00.46,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,but there's just too many.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.46,0:05:04.71,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Just wait until graduation comes\Naround and I pay them back in full.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.71,0:05:08.51,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,When the time comes, Okazaki, I trust you to watch my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.51,0:05:10.38,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Lucky! I'll be sure to bury the knife in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.38,0:05:11.68,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Don't come after me! Go after them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:13.75,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But I'm on the rugby club's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:14.72,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Since when?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.72,0:05:15.93,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Only for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.93,0:05:17.27,Default,Rug,0,0,0,,Keep it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.35,0:05:21.83,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Should I kick back?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.78,0:05:27.71,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Like that, another ordinary day ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.71,0:05:29.04,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.04,0:05:30.27,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,We don't serve that here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.27,0:05:35.14,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's not like I have a goal or something to devote my passion towards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.91,0:05:37.49,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,A bland day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:35.91,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll pray to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.59,0:05:38.12,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Praying won't change things!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.24,0:05:42.89,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,This is a world that has ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.64,0:05:46.41,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,Nothing is born; nothing dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.08,0:05:49.48,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,Even time does not exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.43,0:05:56.57,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,If I were to choose a place to be born,\Nthen I believe that it would not be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.97,0:06:00.68,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,There is a person in a world such as this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.11,0:06:04.02,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,Could she see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:07.04,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,My being has yet to be born into this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:13.22,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,The girl who lives alone in a world that ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:19.20,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,The girl who lives in a vacant, unmoving world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.93,0:06:24.30,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,For a reason I cannot explain, she interests me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.80,0:06:34.78,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Okazaki and Sunohara aren't here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.78,0:06:39.52,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,What are they thinking? They're seniors. Don't they have exams and their futures to worry about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:40.91,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Forget about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.91,0:06:44.19,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,We don't have the time to worry about others, do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.19,0:06:43.83,Default-alt,Guy,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.92,0:06:53.21,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,U-Um, Okazaki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:56.24,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What is it, Fujibayashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:58.80,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,You came in late today, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:06:59.83,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.83,0:07:03.87,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Um, I think you should\Ncome to school properly every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:07.34,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So you talk like a class representative, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.34,0:07:09.73,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,N-Not just “like”,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.12,0:07:11.94,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,I {\i1}am{\i0\fscx30.303} {\r} the class representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.94,0:07:14.31,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Hey, Okazaki. Don't make the class rep cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.31,0:07:16.05,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Her sis is gonna come running in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.05,0:07:18.39,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,I'm fine. I'm not crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.39,0:07:22.63,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Fine. Let's just say it'll depend on tomorrow's mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.63,0:07:26.02,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Th-Then um… I'll read your fortune for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.02,0:07:27.90,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Fortune-telling is a hobby of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.03,0:07:32.85,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Come on…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.85,0:07:35.46,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Okazaki-kun, you'll be late tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.96,0:07:38.67,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Are you picking a fight with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.67,0:07:40.21,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,That's how the cards came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.21,0:07:42.33,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,I think this is sort of how fortune-telling works.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.33,0:07:43.62,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,“Think”?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.62,0:07:48.88,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,On the way to school, you'll have\Na romantic meeting with a kind girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:52.25,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,forget about the time passing by, and therefore be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.25,0:07:54.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's really detailed, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:56.78,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,I-It's a maiden's inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:07:58.47,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Hey! Okazaki Tomoya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.86,0:08:04.19,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.19,0:08:04.85,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Kyou…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:08.83,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You've got some nerve to pick on my little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.21,0:08:10.84,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.84,0:08:12.78,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I was only talking to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:15.78,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Yeah, Onee-chan. He wasn't picking on me or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:19.66,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Then fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:23.92,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You had Ryou read your fortune?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:28.33,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah. Apparently I'm going to have\Na romantic meeting with a kind girl tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:32.32,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What's with the grin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:33.54,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.54,0:08:35.34,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Well, good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.27,0:08:45.84,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So, where shall I eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:47.18,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,A ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.18,0:08:49.14,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Yeah, I heard it appears sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.14,0:08:51.81,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,The ghost of the girl that got in a car accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.81,0:08:53.23,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,I bet it's something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.23,0:08:55.73,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,I'm not kidding! And I heard she's cute, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:55.04,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,A ghost, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.59,0:09:01.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey. You alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:04.91,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why not eat in class with your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:08.00,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sweet bean bread?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:09.87,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:13.61,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'm eating right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:15.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.16,0:09:34.51,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um, how can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:38.28,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask why you're eating lunch out here alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.19,0:09:42.11,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Do you like this school?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:44.20,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Not particularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:47.25,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I really, really love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:53.08,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I used to have friends and teachers I got along with, but now…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.08,0:09:54.27,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:59.47,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Last year, I was away from school for a long period of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:00.54,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,So I'm…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.25,0:10:02.22,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're repeating.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,0:10:05.37,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm repeating.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:14.73,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,All the people I knew graduated,\Nand the everyone left are strangers to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.73,0:10:17.73,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I feel like Urashima Tarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.73,0:10:17.73,Note,Note,0,0,0,,Note: Urashima Tarou is a story in which the protagonist jumps forward in time and finds no one he knew alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:23.85,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. What am I saying to a person I just met…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:26.55,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So that's why you were mumbling that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.57,0:10:29.52,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You weren't involved in any club?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.82,0:10:33.94,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No. I originally wanted to join the drama club,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.94,0:10:38.85,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,but I'm weak and don't think I'd be able to participate in the activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.85,0:10:41.36,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Participate to the extent you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.36,0:10:43.59,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why not go to the drama club after school?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.59,0:10:44.73,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.73,0:10:45.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, look over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.01,0:10:47.68,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,They're looking over at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.68,0:10:51.68,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If you always look so sad, you won't make any friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:53.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Smile and wave your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.26,0:10:56.39,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Come on, with a big smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.57,0:11:03.37,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I guess they didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:07.37,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I don't have much of a presence in class, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.79,0:11:13.10,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,What is that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.96,0:11:21.63,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Wow, so cool! They're wheeling around!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.63,0:11:23.67,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sunohara, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.67,0:11:25.64,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I think they're here for a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:28.91,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Guys from another school are here on bikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:31.71,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing on top of my head?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.39,0:11:36.81,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Is she going to give them a lecture?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:48.49,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Why did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.49,0:11:52.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,This is, after all, the best school in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.07,0:11:53.83,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So there are guys who don't like that idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:56.43,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You're going to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.43,0:11:58.35,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I can't just sit and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.35,0:12:00.30,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about Tomoyo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:01.32,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Tomoyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:02.63,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,You don't know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.63,0:12:04.55,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,She just transferred in as a junior this spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.55,0:12:06.71,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Sakagami Tomoyo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.71,0:12:08.23,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,She's really strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.23,0:12:10.51,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,If you go out, you might just get in her way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.51,0:12:12.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:14.56,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I don't want to cause an unnecessary disturbance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:16.56,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Get lost before you get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:19.08,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,If you do, I'll let all of you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:22.67,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,You don't want to deliberately ask for pain, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.67,0:12:24.11,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Don't screw with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.26,0:12:48.68,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Don't screw with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.60,0:12:53.30,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:53.30,Default-alt,Girls,0,0,0,,So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.14,0:12:56.60,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,What is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.60,0:13:00.31,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,So she's a transfer student…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.31,0:13:04.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Her situation is similar to yours, and yet she's still so popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.05,0:13:06.34,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So everything depends on the individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.34,0:13:08.90,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Maybe you are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.42,0:13:10.89,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Who do I think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.89,0:13:13.44,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm in no position to lecture others.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.44,0:13:14.30,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:17.43,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.91,0:13:18.84,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:19.43,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:21.38,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:25.88,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm Okazaki Tomoya from Class D.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:29.08,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm Furukawa Nagisa from Class B.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.08,0:13:30.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.31,0:13:33.88,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, nice to meet you, too, Okazaki Tomoya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.88,0:13:34.78,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Hey, Okazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.23,0:13:38.99,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Tag along later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.94,0:13:42.87,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,A setup?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.87,0:13:46.48,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Yeah, there's no way a girl can beat guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.48,0:13:50.23,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You paid them to lose to help\Nmake yourself popular or something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.23,0:13:52.77,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,If it's not money, would it be the other something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:57.08,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Girls are lucky, since stupid guys will buy into that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.08,0:13:58.73,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:14:00.30,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,They're the gang from the senior class.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.30,0:14:02.18,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,I think they're Sunohara and Okazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.18,0:14:06.91,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Rejoice. I was thinking I wouldn't hurt those in the same school,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.91,0:14:09.38,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,but I will make an exception and specially fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.38,0:14:11.74,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Acting tough like that is so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:13.61,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I bet your knees are shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.61,0:14:15.73,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I would like to make this self-defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.73,0:14:16.70,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,So you come at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:19.25,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Don't be so full of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.18,0:14:22.97,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.97,0:14:25.33,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's when I remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.72,0:14:30.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,In this city, there used to be a really strong, beautiful girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:35.20,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,who went around beating up people who troubled ordinary folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:37.25,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So the rumor goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.25,0:14:38.99,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Tell me earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.99,0:14:40.91,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,{\an8}She's so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.99,0:14:40.91,Default-alt,Girls,0,0,0,,{\an8}That guy's so lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.77,0:14:41.22,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Please don't come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.18,0:14:43.87,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.99,0:14:47.42,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Third floor of the old building.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.42,0:14:50.76,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly, this is where\Nthe liberal arts club rooms are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.17,0:14:54.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Looks like she's up to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.68,0:14:58.20,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hamburger?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:14:59.84,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.45,0:15:15.77,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.77,0:15:17.35,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I didn't know you were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:18.09,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.78,0:15:20.73,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,What's this hand for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.12,0:15:22.54,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No real reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:25.46,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I had forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.46,0:15:29.13,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The drama club closed down in March.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.13,0:15:32.88,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I heard the number of members was small to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.01,0:15:41.90,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But since they're only closed,\Nonce conditions are met, it can start up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.90,0:15:43.71,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Do you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:45.76,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why not give it another try?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.76,0:15:47.26,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll help you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:48.94,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um, Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.74,0:15:54.70,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Why are you being so kind to me when we've just met?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.28,0:15:56.90,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.90,0:15:58.33,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I wonder why, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.65,0:16:18.17,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,Sit when you eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.41,0:16:24.77,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,We'll part here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:26.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Okay. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.21,0:16:28.02,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um, Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:32.47,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,My house is the bakery further ahead, in front of the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.47,0:16:34.91,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Please come when you feel like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:36.13,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, when I feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.46,0:16:39.03,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.03,0:16:40.94,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What? No one's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.40,0:16:46.58,San,San,0,0,0,,That's this week's new release.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.58,0:16:48.54,San,San,0,0,0,,Please try one if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.54,0:16:50.46,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Furukawa's older sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:51.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Or mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:53.56,San,San,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about paying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.56,0:16:54.76,San,San,0,0,0,,Since it's a leftover.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.76,0:16:57.38,San,San,0,0,0,,The concept for that is “soothing”.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.38,0:16:58.68,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Soothing…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:17:01.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then I'll take the offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.14,0:17:08.64,San,San,0,0,0,,There's a rice cracker inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.64,0:17:11.32,San,San,0,0,0,,It's rice cracker bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:15.70,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The naming sense is startling,\Nbut your sense for making bread is startling, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:16.99,San,San,0,0,0,,You think so, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:22.10,San,San,0,0,0,,Then the idea turned out well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.63,0:17:25.99,San,San,0,0,0,,Um, is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.99,0:17:27.12,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You want to hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.12,0:17:30.25,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,To put it bluntly, this is a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.96,0:17:35.26,San,San,0,0,0,,It wasn't good?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.26,0:17:38.17,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,There is a problem with the taste,\Nbut first of all, it's too difficult to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.17,0:17:40.71,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's natural that you get leftovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.47,0:17:47.71,San,San,0,0,0,,So my… my bread is…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:49.09,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,H-Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:52.16,San,San,0,0,0,,It was natural there would be leftovers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.48,0:17:55.33,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Like mother, like daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.33,0:17:58.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I hope the father is sane.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.31,0:17:59.52,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.52,0:18:00.36,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.36,0:18:01.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Well, this sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.92,0:18:04.07,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You said what you're not supposed to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:07.60,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You should have kept eating and said it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.41,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,That's what duty is about. What morality is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.41,0:18:12.05,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,The truth is always harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.05,0:18:15.34,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,And, to tell her that so straightforwardly,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.34,0:18:16.34,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,would be too brutal for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.85,0:18:19.65,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,The neighbors all eat her bread saying it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.65,0:18:20.98,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,This is an unspoken rule!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.98,0:18:21.84,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,It's law!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.84,0:18:23.68,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,So you'd better obey it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:25.10,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Or else I'll knock you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.91,0:18:29.09,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You're wearing the same uniform as our daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.09,0:18:31.83,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you're Nagisa's friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.41,0:18:34.31,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Should've told me earlier, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:38.61,San,San,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I presented myself so shamefully before my daughter's friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:40.35,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Sanae.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.35,0:18:43.21,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,He looks dumb, so I bet he forgot about it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.21,0:18:43.84,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.84,0:18:46.20,San,San,0,0,0,,You shouldn't say that to our guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:47.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why is it turning out like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.80,0:18:49.45,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,In any case, it's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.45,0:18:52.72,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Nagisa brought a friend over\Nas soon as the new semester started.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.72,0:18:54.83,San,San,0,0,0,,And a boy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.83,0:18:56.16,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.16,0:18:57.45,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,A guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.45,0:18:58.48,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You just noticed now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.48,0:19:01.26,San,San,0,0,0,,Maybe he's her boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:04.86,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I can't give Nagisa away to a puny guy like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.86,0:19:05.61,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.61,0:19:07.57,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.91,0:19:06.61,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Shoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.57,0:19:09.26,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You really call yourself a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.26,0:19:12.62,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,If you're a man, sweep away the woman\Nyou fell in love with even if it means using force.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.62,0:19:14.10,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,That said, I still won't give her to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:18.30,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You're all getting along already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:21.50,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Of course. We'd never mistreat our daughter's friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.50,0:19:22.63,Default,3,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.28,0:19:25.57,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,What's with the blank look?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.57,0:19:29.86,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I was thinking that I probably shouldn't get myself involved with this family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:34.08,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,As you can see, we can already fire slightly harsh jokes at each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.08,0:19:37.30,San,San,0,0,0,,Oh right, we haven't heard your name yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.30,0:19:38.52,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,He's Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.52,0:19:39.59,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki Tomoya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.26,0:19:42.22,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,What a puny name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.22,0:19:43.90,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Make it like Okazaki Ginga!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.22,0:19:43.90,Note,Note,0,0,0,,Note: Ginga = Galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.90,0:19:45.35,San,San,0,0,0,,That is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:47.91,San,San,0,0,0,,May I call you Ginga-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:50.27,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,While you're at it, change your family name to Daiuchuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:50.27,Note,Note,0,0,0,,Note: Daiuchuu = Cosmos
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.27,0:19:51.50,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Daiuchuu Ginga.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:52.52,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Great name, ain't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:54.78,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,My name is Okazaki Tomoya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:57.20,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,What a picky brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.20,0:19:59.71,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Sanae, do you have any good names?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.71,0:20:01.06,San,San,0,0,0,,Let's see…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.40,0:20:04.57,San,San,0,0,0,,How about adding something after his given name?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.57,0:20:09.05,San,San,0,0,0,,Something not only large, but a word that says\Nhe's a being that has surpassed the flow of time…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.05,0:20:11.01,San,San,0,0,0,,Okazaki Tomoya Eternal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.64,0:20:13.00,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.00,0:20:15.10,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,That's your name from now on, Ethanol.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.10,0:20:16.29,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It changed…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.91,0:20:37.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Thank you. I know the way back from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.69,0:20:40.59,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Sorry we made you stay so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.51,0:20:43.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It was a strange experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.57,0:20:45.76,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So there are families like that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.07,0:20:48.13,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You guys get along so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.13,0:20:49.36,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.36,0:20:51.83,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I think we're normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.79,0:20:54.12,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.12,0:20:56.41,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.41,0:21:02.87,Default-alt,TV,0,0,0,,{\an8}On the 27th, the distance between Earth and Mars will be close to 55.75 million kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.77,0:21:16.23,Default-alt,TV,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx98}Mars is a planet that revolves outside of Earth's orbit, and due to the rotation rates, the distance will be closer than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.77,0:21:06.67,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Pops, if you're going to sleep, you should lie down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:08.91,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.18,0:21:15.39,Oka,OkaF,0,0,0,,Oh, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.23,0:21:19.37,Oka,OkaF,0,0,0,,I guess I caused Tomoya-kun some trouble again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.65,0:21:28.61,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,My mother died in a car accident when I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.99,0:21:34.57,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Possibly because of that, Pops fell into alcohol and gambling, and stopped working.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.94,0:21:46.00,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,If you wish…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.18,0:21:53.14,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,…would you like me to take you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.11,0:21:58.72,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,To a place in this city where wishes come true.
