Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.65,0:23:43.59,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Okazaki, let's skip school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.59,0:23:45.85,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,It's Saturday, so it's a half day anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.08,0:23:52.69,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'll finish it right away, so please wait in the club room.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.53,0:23:55.57,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.57,0:23:57.20,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,No dents.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.20,0:23:59.07,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,I'll let you off without paying the repair fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.07,0:24:00.49,Fuk,Fuk,0,0,0,,Fuuko made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.55,0:24:04.16,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.16,0:24:05.34,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Forget what I said.
